			<a href="mailto:garethlegrange+work@gmail.com?subject=Work%20with%20me" class="text-sm text-balance font-normal leading-none tracking-wide bg-transparent text-neutral-900 border border-neutral-700 rounded-full py-2 px-4 flex gap-x-2 items-center">
