					<svg class="fill-neutral-900" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="#643341" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path d="M224,48H32a8,8,0,0,0-8,8V192a16,16,0,0,0,16,16H216a16,16,0,0,0,16-16V56A8,8,0,0,0,224,48Zm-96,85.15L52.57,64H203.43ZM98.71,128,40,181.81V74.19Zm11.84,10.85,12,11.05a8,8,0,0,0,10.82,0l12-11.05,58,53.15H52.57ZM157.29,128,216,74.18V181.82Z"></path></svg>
